version_description:
We hope you are all well and safe at home. In the meantime, we have got you colorful tags for your reposts and text color as well. You can now set your suitable color according to your repost. Hope you will find this feature useful.
Added Appearance option in the Settings if you want to change Dark/Light mode.
Added Passcode security to your app for your privacy.
We also fixed some know bugs and make app improvement.

Feel free to contact if you have any suggestions or queries for us.
